OL,3,CMum of teen killed in car crash voices
OL,4,Canger over government's driving reforms
OL,6,FMs Owen has campaigned for the
OL,7,Fintroduction of graduated driving
OL,8,Flicences, which would include a ban on
OL,9,Fyoung drivers carrying young
OL,10,Fpassengers unless an adult is with
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,FShe told ITV's Good Morning Britain:
OL,14,F"As a parent, I was not able to keep
OL,15,Fhim safe on that day because the
OL,16,Fbiggest risk to young people is
OL,17,Fgetting into a car with their friends."
OL,19,FMs Owen said more restrictions on
OL,20,Fyounger drivers could have saved her
OL,21,Fson.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
