OL,3,CMum of teen killed in car crash voices
OL,4,Canger over government's driving reforms
OL,6,F"The coroner did rule that the crash
OL,7,Fwas due to the actions of the driver,
OL,8,Fso they said that the graduated
OL,9,Flicense would have prevented this.
OL,11,F"And they also stated that if the
OL,12,Fgovernment do not put extra safety
OL,13,Fmeasures in place, young people will
OL,14,Fcontinue to die on the roads, and
OL,15,Fthat's what's so frustrating."
OL,17,FMs Owen was among the parents of road
OL,18,Fcrash victims who delivered a 100,000-
OL,19,Fsignature petition to Downing Street
OL,20,Fin April calling for the change.
